articles.title: Inntober 2021 #06: "Spirit" - A Bartender Running Low On Spirits

frontMatter.title: Inntober 2021 #06: "Spirit" - A Bartender Running Low On Spirits

articles.rawContent:
2021 was a busy year for me and this is the only thing I finished for [Inktober](https://inktober.com/rules).

![Sad Gnolls Club](/img/posts/inntober-2021-06-spirit/sad-gnolls-club-04-with-vest.png)

Featuring [Rufelt](https://thewanderinginn.fandom.com/wiki/Rufelt_Owelt) and [Belavierr](https://thewanderinginn.fandom.com/wiki/Belavierr) from [The Wandering Inn](https://wanderinginn.com/).

Made in [FireAlpaca](https://firealpaca.com/).
